---
title: Hoisin Sweet Potato & Mushroom Bowls with Ginger Rice & Sriracha Soy Mayo
description: Tonight, we’ve got a meal that’ll leave you feeling totally zen. This dinner is a one-bowl veggie treat that won’t disappoint. Here, hoisin-and-sesame-glazed sweet potatoes and mushrooms, roasted bell pepper, spicy soy mayo, and a scattering of sesame seeds are all served over a heap of fluffy, gingery rice. You’re one bite away from inner dinner peace.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/615db700beeacb7f92644b10-833d47c7.jpg
